{"tid":412582,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"凍齡美魔女關之琳　三十年無變過","createTime":"2017-09-24T18:58:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-25T05:07:39.000Z","uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"302dc5288e7e90a7aaafd0283d299bbf94a856e1","tid":412582,"uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T18:58:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/25/025820_bab6adeccde6532ebb75cd61bc5df5fc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F25%2F025820_bab6adeccde6532ebb75cd61bc5df5fc.jpg&h=afc7942f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n55歲的美魔女關之琳有香江第一美人之稱，八十年代入行的她至今仍然是一位大美人，臉上毫無歲月的痕跡，身形及外貌皆保養得宜，入行至今足足防腐三十年！當年關之琳以一臉精緻的五官突圍而出，及後參演不同的電視及電影作品，大獲好評，1988年參演《最佳損友闖情關》時已十分驚艷，及後更憑1991年的電影《婚姻勿語》於第11屆香港電影金像獎獲提名最佳女配角，展示美人紮實的演技。至2015年她到台灣人氣清談節目《康熙來了》受訪，她的美貌始終如一。美魔女曾大方分享凍齡秘訣，就是要堅持打扮及保養，坦言是對自己的尊重。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2xp89qp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2xp89qp&d=oymE8WJClX8JhFwnOdnowE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=deee17a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2xp89qp</a>"},{"pid":"7183957f69c86c5bd71fd6b10cec97b7c328bbb1","tid":412582,"uid":48577,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T20:12:30.000Z","msg":"以前睇佢已經覺得唔靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2ea49de3eebae4b3a3aac4e8734a6748c7f7771","tid":412582,"uid":10661,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T20:39:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前睇佢已經覺得唔靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好似狐狸，一啲都唔靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee56b6b8a726a4ff97c32e47f0994320ce1696c5","tid":412582,"uid":69877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T20:45:32.000Z","msg":"好膠塊面"},{"pid":"953b8681a52106202708ce47da203e40e440dec2","tid":412582,"uid":82